reviewText: It's Jerry Lewis ! No more needs to be said ! Lmbo...every movie!
Have been a Jerry Lewis fan since I was a small child. So, love having four of his movies in once package! Will watch over and over again!! And these are some of his best!!
Love it. This movie is to funny. I'm happy with the delivery. And right on time.
It was just what he wanted.

4 of the best Jerry Lewis movies ever made.. Everybody LOVES The Nutty Professor, along with the others In This 4 pack . Great movies by a great entertainer, Funny, wholesome, family entertainment that is still enjoyable 50 years after it was made. I have enjoyed these movies all my life, and now I watch them with my grandchildren. You won't be sorry ordering this set ..
I love this DVD.  All of the movies are good and I've enjoyed them several times.  I especially like The Nutty Professor; Cinderfella, and The Family Jewels.

I won't say too much about this collection except for this...hysterical. Jerry Lewis had his own brand of very silly and slapstick humor that worked so well for him and probably would not for others. Each of these 4 movies were at different times moving, sweet and very funny. I wholeheartedly recommend them.
Gave as a gift, my mother grew up with these movies and loves watching them.
Funniest guy ever. Huuuuuuuuge jerry lewis fan. P.S. I love you Jerry Lewis !
JERRY IS SO OFF THE WALL !!  FUN MOVIES !!
